name: Bitning Bolt
description: Fonxo designed this powerful Bitcoin lightning Bolt (Bitning Bolt) from scratch, he was struck by the power of knowledge and decided to move forward in this minimalism design. This lightining represents the velocity of the evolving world in an always changing environment. It represents the freedom of the humanity and tries to emerge from the nothing. It is a piece of art composed by 500x700 pixels exactly.
